1
[h2 id=Rulesinsubmittingmovies 
	"Rules in submitting movies
	$LF
]h2
[p 
	"We accept these movies:
	$LF
]p
[ul 
	[li 
		" Famtasia movie files (FMV) (NES / Famicom)
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" snes9x movie files (SMV) (SNES / Super Famicom)
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Gens movie files (GMV) (Sega Genesis)
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[p 
	"Nothing else is accepted.
	$LF
	"We also don't accept multimedia files (AVI, WMV and so on) for various reasons.
	$LF
]p
[h2 id=Rulesintool-assistedmoviemaking 
	"Rules in tool-assisted movie making
	$LF
]h2
[h3 id=FamtasiaisNTSC-thegameshouldbeNTSCaswell. 
	"Famtasia is NTSC - the game should be NTSC as well.
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"PAL NES games (most European games) are not allowed, unless the
	$LF
	"USA version does not work.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"The problem is that PAL versions play 20% too fast.
	$LF
]p
[h3 id=Thegamesmustbereal 
	"The games must be real
	$LF
]h3
[pre 
	$LF
]pre
[p 
	"The movie should look like it could have been played with
	$LF
	"an authentic hardware. This makes it more familiar to the
	$LF
	"audience.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"This details to the following points:
	$LF
]p
[pre 
	$LF
]pre
[h4 id=Hackedgamesarenotallowed 
	"Hacked games are not allowed
	$LF
]h4
[pre 
	"  
	$LF
]pre
[p 
	"An exception to this are hacks which only make the
	$LF
	"game playable on an emulator.
	$LF
]p
[pre 
	$LF
]pre
[h4 id=Gamegeniecodesetcarenotallowed 
	"Game genie codes etc are not allowed
	$LF
]h4
[h4 id=Cheat-keysanddebuggingcodesarenotallowed 
	"Cheat-keys and debugging codes are not allowed
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"Such as Konami's up+up+down+down+etc sequence.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"If the key sequence is mentioned in the manual as a normal
	$LF
	"means of playing, it is (usually) allowed.
	$LF
]p
[h4 id=Out-of-emulationpostprocessing,suchasvideoediting,isnotallowed 
	"Out-of-emulation postprocessing, such as video editing, is not allowed
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"(Non-gameplay-altering edits such as adding subtitles
	$LF
	"are not forbidden.)
]p
